{"tid":2193081,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"12歲少女被膝壓　媽媽批警「砌生豬肉」票控　今日重看片段感心痛","createTime":"2020-09-07T14:19:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T16:57:28.000Z","uid":240362,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9feb6ca39f578cafe06dcc177d106011b970f3e0","tid":2193081,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T14:19:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=366394427695406\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D366394427695406&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqA8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=ca01a66c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=366394427695406</a><br />\n<br />\n昨天9月6日是原定的立法會選舉投票日，抗議選舉延期一年的市民，昨午去到油尖旺區，但警方嚴密佈防，拘捕了至少289人，又以「限聚令」票控117人。警方昨日行動中，一名12歲少女被防暴警員飛身撲倒，警員更騎在少女腰上，令人譁然。少女與同行的20歲哥哥被指違反「限聚令」收到罰款告票。<br />\n<br />\n兩兄妹的媽媽何太今午接受港台電台節目訪問，重組事件經過。何太指讀中一的女兒當時只是去買顏料，兩兄妹身上只有手機和銀包，行到西洋菜南街時，一隊警員從他們面前經過，但有一、兩個警員突然回頭喊道：「企喺度，唔好郁！」妹妹被黑衫持棍警員呼喝受驚，遂急步走開，不料迎面有個防暴警突然撲來。兄妹二人其後連同一個中年男子被指違反「限聚令」。何太形容，兄妹與男子不相識，男子只是在旁叫警員不要這樣對女生，就被警員拉入來與兄妹湊夠3人「違反限聚令」。兩兄妹在醫院驗傷後證實無大礙，何太表示今日重看影片才「識得心痛」，妹妹今日則不願意提起這件事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/33670/%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F-12%E6%AD%B2%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3-96%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-33670/12%E6%AD%B2%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E8%A2%AB%E8%86%9D%E5%A3%93-%E5%AA%BD%E5%AA%BD%E6%89%B9%E8%AD%A6%E3%80%8C%E7%A0%8C%E7%94%9F%E8%B1%AC%E8%82%89%E3%80%8D%E7%A5%A8%E6%8E%A7-%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E9%87%8D%E7%9C%8B%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5%E6%84%9F%E5%BF%83%E7%97%9B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F33670%2F%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F-12%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3-96%25E4%25B9%259D%25E9%25BE%258D%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-33670%2F12%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%2586%259D%25E5%25A3%2593-%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E6%2589%25B9%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%25A0%258C%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25B1%25AC%25E8%2582%2589%25E3%2580%258D%25E7%25A5%25A8%25E6%258E%25A7-%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%2597%25A5%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%259C%258B%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E6%2584%259F%25E5%25BF%2583%25E7%2597%259B&d=nUkjSwirbxPTmroveKClqA8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=a701e6ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/33670/%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F-12%E6%AD%B2%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3-96%E4%B9%9D%E9%BE%8D%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-33670/12%E6%AD%B2%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3%E8%A2%AB%E8%86%9D%E5%A3%93-%E5%AA%BD%E5%AA%BD%E6%89%B9%E8%AD%A6%E3%80%8C%E7%A0%8C%E7%94%9F%E8%B1%AC%E8%82%89%E3%80%8D%E7%A5%A8%E6%8E%A7-%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E9%87%8D%E7%9C%8B%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5%E6%84%9F%E5%BF%83%E7%97%9B</a>"},{"pid":"2bbba7afcc46ee0c33391ffdd00f07c549ed09db","tid":2193081,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T14:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db937b589e1aae53f90bbf1073fe382441d8fa97","tid":2193081,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2bbba7afcc46ee0c33391ffdd00f07c549ed09db","tid":2193081,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T14:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T14:19:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19e7af20674c6844595038104d7c8349baf62d60","tid":2193081,"uid":228955,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T14:20:52.000Z","msg":"希望佢娘親係藍"},{"pid":"c58a69928bf865427d4d19f00526d43500d7ca5a","tid":2193081,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T14:23:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91795f366c5f599ad7e590fefc1f6dc6fb19553a","tid":2193081,"uid":183844,"like":2,